    <status value="extensions"/><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>urn:VAST</code><table class="none"><tr><td style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href="ConceptMap-CMVFLocationStatus.html">VF_LocationStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>A</td><td>Active</td><td><span title="EQUIVALENT">~</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-active">active</a></td></tr><tr><td>D</td><td>Permanently Deactivated</td><td><span title="EQUIVALENT">~</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-inactive">inactive</a></td></tr><tr><td>P</td><td>Planned</td><td><span title="EQUIVALENT">~</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-null">null</a><i>(There is no code for planned in FHIR)</i></td></tr><tr><td>T</td><td>Temporarily Deactivated</td><td><span title="EQUIVALENT">~</span><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-suspended">suspended</a></td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html"><code>http://hl7.org/fhir/location-status</code></a><table class="none"><tr><td style="white-space:nowrap"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href="ConceptMap-CMVFLocationStatus.html">VF_LocationStatus</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-active">active</a></td><td>Active</td><td>The location is operational.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-inactive">inactive</a></td><td>Inactive</td><td>The location is no longer used.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-null">null</a></td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-location-status.html#location-status-suspended">suspended</a></td><td>Suspended</td><td>The location is temporarily closed.</td><td/></tr></table></li></ul></div>
